{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d0a2978de5","title":"省、市委书记会议上各同志提出的问题","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7cdfa8de0b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":23,"articleId":"d0a2978de5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7fc5fd78be","name":"中共中央办公厅"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"410df1aa74","type":"title","text":"省、市委书记会议上各同志提出的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"0378a21bd1","type":"authors","text":"中共中央办公厅","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"25040b33f4","type":"appellation","text":"黄火青：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"c3ce5768b2","type":"paragraph","text":"一、天津电力供应紧张，希望在投资上加以照顾。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"a2e66a3436","type":"paragraph","text":"二、原材料如果不能保证人民生活最低限度的需要，基本建设投资应当进一步削减。对原材料的分配应当首先照顾维护和修理的需要。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"a823349fcb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、减薪问题要慎重，同意几年之内不再增加，并且提倡多买公债。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"0659c1dcd2","type":"paragraph","text":"四、中小学实行二部制以后，应当适应新情况，加强课外活动的辅导制度，适当增加辅导人员。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"e7d0af67e4","type":"paragraph","text":"五、高等学校经费统一由高等教育部管理，不便于解决各部门所属学校的具体困难，希望研究改进的办法。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"293d06a94d","type":"paragraph","text":"六、主张在机关肃反完成以后接着进行合营企业的肃反工作，不要停顿。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"f4b69965d8","type":"appellation","text":"陆定一：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"8cf55f65ca","type":"paragraph","text":"一、建议全国领导干部从今年开始学习辨证法。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"5d3a5705e7","type":"appellation","text":"周小舟：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"393112f72a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、法制问题上已经发生右倾的偏向，希望有关部门注意纠正。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"ba801beb74","type":"appellation","text":"吴德：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"dbd835f345","type":"paragraph","text":"一、吉林去年死马二十一万匹，主要原因是饲料不足，负担过重，管理不善，希望增加饲料的留量。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"e8afba5c59","type":"paragraph","text":"二、希望把各地拖拉机站的农业机器，集中起来，组织复员军人开垦荒地。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"1d886ae227","type":"paragraph","text":"三、吉林乡干部的收入不比农民高多少，但是他们的支出要比一般农民多，因此，不宜全国一律降低，应当由各地按照不同情况分别适当处理。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"abf81e75b9","type":"appellation","text":"邓子恢：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"88b9ed6d22","type":"paragraph","text":"一、应当适当地缩小粮食的地区差价，提高山区的粮食价格。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"cecfc28e85","type":"paragraph","text":"二、地方上的商业机构过多，有的县有十四个事业公司，应当合并。省、专、县三级对商业工作应当有适当的权力。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"00cc1cec2d","type":"paragraph","text":"三、为了改善耕畜的饲养，促进耕畜的繁殖，希望各省认真研究和解决有关提高价格、留出草料基地恢复牛行等问题。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"86886b3c7e","type":"paragraph","text":"四、第二个五年计划的农林水方面的投资，希望保持八大规定的比例，不要降低。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"b8faeb0453","type":"paragraph","text":"五、福建各县的负责干部中，外来干部太多，本地干部过少，应当采取办法，适当调整。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"c3f0d98caa","type":"paragraph","text":"六、关于区乡划分问题，提议撤乡留区，把区划小。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"},{"id":"ecbd6e3792","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央办公厅机要室　一九五七年一月二十四日发","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5"}],"page":{"id":"d2da78a36f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d0a2978de5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}